{"title":"金色的油砂","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":4,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的油砂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细得象一根针眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小得如一粒芝麻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千粒千颗汇成一团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱含热能的精华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地层里藏了千万年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们心中日夜盼挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于问世了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠江盆地的第一颗油砂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在荧光屏上细看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉得你小中有大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象一颗金色的星辰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人兴奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引人进发！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报告南海油田的黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人晶莹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映人光华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又似一粒闪光的砝码，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掂着南海的富饶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油井的代价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又如钻工一颗红心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈、透明，春光焕发！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——啊，金色的油砂……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}